                    <p>Moba, and its affiliates, parents, and subsidiaries (&quot;Moba&quot; or &quot;we&quot;, &quot;us&quot;, or the &quot;Company&quot;) take your privacy seriously. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, share, and protect your Personal Information. If you do not want us to handle your Personal Information in this manner, please do not use the Moba Platform. Personal Information is information that relates to you as an individually identifiable person, such as your name, e-mail address, and mobile number.</p>
