                    <p>This Privacy Policy applies only to (a) information that we collect on the websites moba.com.ng, (collectively, the <strong>&quot;Site&quot;</strong>) and (b) through the Moba mobile applications, including the mobile application for service requesters and the mobile application for service professionals (the <strong>&quot;App&quot;</strong>) (collectively the <strong>&quot;Moba Platform&quot;</strong>).</p>
                    <p>&nbsp;</p>
                    <h3>I. INFORMATION WE COLLECT</h3>
                    <h3>a) Personal Information You Give Us</h3>
                    <p>We collect information that you voluntarily share with us through the Moba Platform.</p>
                    <p>If you are using the Moba Platform to request professional services, or contact Moba or its third-party service providers, you may give us:</p>
